    <item>
      <title>刺激计划疑虑导致中国股市创 2020 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/chinese-stocks-slump-amid-stimulus-skepticism-weak-holiday-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员对北京方面刺激措施的步伐感到不耐烦，且疲软的假日消费数据打击了市场人气，中国在岸上市的股票遭遇了四年多来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/chinese-stocks-slump-amid-stimulus-skepticism-weak-holiday-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 01:35:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞穗购买“安全”资产以应对美国软着陆失败的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/mizuho-buys-safe-assets-to-cut-damage-if-us-soft-landing-fails</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果投资者对美国经济软着陆的预测被证明是错误的，瑞穗金融集团将通过囤积美国国债等易于出售的资产来应对短期市场混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/mizuho-buys-safe-assets-to-cut-damage-if-us-soft-landing-fails</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
